name: 2.2.0.Final
body:
- [**closed**] Apicurio registry base URL not working [#2138](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/2138)
- [**closed**] Search by property value is not returning any results [#2125](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/2125)
- [**Question**] CORS configuration [#2106](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/2106)
- [**Question**] [Question] New release of apicurio-registry-protobuf-schema-utilities [#1956](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/1956)
- [**closed**] Support for Java 8 [#1896](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/1896)
- [**Bug**] The KafkaSql storage throws exception when querying contentIdFromHash: `Expected one element, but found none` [#1873](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/1873)
- [**Question**] Does Apicurio support Java 17 [#1838](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/1838)
- [**Bug**] Unsupported operation in OIDC http client [#1796](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/1796)
- [**Enhancement**] Ensure authentication failure to API is properly formatted [#1126](https://github.com/Apicurio/apicurio-registry/issues/1126)
